org.codehaus.jackson.map.deser

Class Creator.Delegating

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codehaus.jackson.map.deser.Creator.Delegating
  • Enclosing class:
    Creator

    static final class Creator.Delegating
extends java.lang.Object
    Creator implementation used for cases where parts of deserialization are delegated to another serializer, by first binding to an intermediate object, and then passing that object to the delegate creator (and then deserializer).
